commit.message:
dyn-string.c: Remove test of IN_LIBGCC2 and IN_GLIBCPP_V3 and the associated #define of...

	* dyn-string.c: Remove test of IN_LIBGCC2 and IN_GLIBCPP_V3 and
	the associated #define of RETURN_ON_ALLOCATION_FAILURE.
